<h1>The African Poets and Poetry in the News</h1>

<%= render "inthenews/top_include" %>

<h2>Events</h2>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-5">
    
    <label for="exampleInput">Search Events</label>
    <div class="input-group">
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Search for...">
      <span class="input-group-btn">
        <button class="btn btn-default" type="button">Go!</button>
      </span>
    </div><!-- /input-group -->

    <p>Select a type of event to see the distribution of the news about these events on the continent.</p>

    <div class="btn-group">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
        Event Type <span class="caret"></span>
      </button>
      <ul class="dropdown-menu">
        <li><a href="#">Professional</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Political</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Social</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Personal</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

 <ul class="timeslider">
      <li>1864</li>
      <li>1920</li>
      <li>1900</li>
      <li>1940</li>
      <li>1960</li>
      <li>1980</li>
      <li>2000</li>
    </ul>
    <p> <br/>Search by decade by sliding the timeline to see the distribution of the Poets who had events in the news during that time period.</p>

   

